OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,FPopstar Shakira has performed in front
OL,7,Fof two million people after a free
OL,8,Fconcert on a Brazilian beach drew in
OL,9,Fhuge crowds.
OL,11,FThe Colombian singer took to the stage
OL,12,Fon Copacabana Beach, in Rio de
OL,13,FJaneiro, around 11pm on Saturday
OL,14,Fnight, as drones flew overhead and
OL,15,Fwrote "I love you Brazil" in
OL,16,FPortuguese in the sky.
OL,18,FThe concert was part of her Las
OL,19,FMujeres Ya No Lloran - Women No Longer
OL,20,FCry - world tour, which is named after
OL,21,Fher 2024 album.
OL,26,@wD@GOUwD@YO]
