OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt follows similar shows by Lady Gaga
OL,12,Flast year and Madonna in 2024, which
OL,13,Fwere also attended by huge numbers of
OL,14,Fpeople dancing on the sand.
OL,16,FShakira told the crowds about the
OL,17,Ffirst time she came to Brazil, some
OL,18,Fthree decades ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
