CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777892572
OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,F"I arrived here when I was 18 years
OL,7,Fold, dreaming about singing for you,"
OL,8,FShakira said shortly after she came on
OL,9,Fstage. "And now look at this. Life is
OL,10,Fmagical."
OL,12,FShakira sang fan favorites such as
OL,13,FHips Don't Lie, La Tortura, and La
OL,14,FBicicleta, and ended her show with the
OL,15,Fsong BZRP Music Sessions _53/66, which
OL,16,Ffollowed her separation from Spanish
OL,17,Ffootball player Gerard Pique.
OL,19,F"Us women, every time we fall we get
OL,20,Fup a little wiser," Shakira said
OL,21,Fduring the performance.
