OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,FRio Mayor Eduardo Cavaliere wrote on X
OL,7,Fthat two million people attended the
OL,8,Fperformance, declaring: "The She-Wolf
OL,9,Fmade history in Rio."
OL,11,FThe free concert is part of City
OL,12,FHall's attempt to boost economic
OL,13,Factivity in the area after Carnival
OL,14,Fand New Year's Eve festivities and
OL,15,Fbefore the monthlong Saint John's Day
OL,16,Fcelebrations in June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
