PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777892572
OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,F"For us, parties are serious business.
OL,7,FBecause parties generate jobs, income,
OL,8,Fdevelopment, and identity for the
OL,9,Fcity," Cavaliere said on Wednesday, as
OL,10,Fhe presented the city's operational
OL,11,Fplan for the event.
OL,13,F"Our investment in this show will give
OL,14,Fus a financial return 40 times
OL,15,Fgreater," he said.
OL,17,FThe performance was expected to
OL,18,Fgenerate around 777 million reais
OL,19,F(around #114 million), according to a
OL,20,Fstudy by City Hall and Riotur, the
OL,21,Fmunicipality's tourism company.
