OL,3,CFree Shakira concert draws crowds of
OL,4,Ctwo million to Brazil beach
OL,6,FIn April, Airbnb said it was seeing an
OL,7,Fincrease in guests travelling to
OL,8,FBrazil from different parts of Latin
OL,9,FAmerica and Europe.
OL,11,FWanderson Andrade, a 30-year-old
OL,12,Farchitect, said he flew in especially
OL,13,Ffor the show from the city of Goiana
OL,14,Fin central Brazil, with plans to fly
OL,15,Fback the following day.
OL,17,F"I tried to get tickets to see her in
OL,18,FBrazil last year but I didn't succeed.
OL,19,FToday is a dream come true," said
OL,20,FAndrade.
